Sentencas: Lowering the sintering temperature of cathode material for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC) is the main concern of current research.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: In the present work, well-known La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 system as cathode for IT-SOFC was prepared by using mechanochemical synthesis by varying the grinding time.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The pure phase La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 forms after dry milling at 24 h with 500 rpm.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: X-ray diffraction confirms single crystalline rhombohedral phase of as-synthesized and sintered La0.9Sr0.1MnO3.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Sintering at 700 degrees C improves the degree of crystallinity.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Scanning electron microscope images of as-synthesized samples reveal highly agglomerate fine-scale grains.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The temperature dependence of DC conductivity curve exhibits linear dependence of conductivity with temperature.
Titulo: Effect of varying milling time on the formation of La0.9Sr0.1MnO3 for IT-SOFC
